This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=1451

This plugin will look in the current directory for aborted subversion commit log messages, and then read in the newest one to your current commit log.

This saves you having to remember what the log files are called, or importing it yourself and tidying up the log message manually.

http://atlee.ca/blog/software/svn-commit/
